                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">원소전투 스킬</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">얼음 원소 피해</span>를 3pt 준다.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/80830045/c815c3f7cfd5d0658dd94a1e28beda8b_262139912988508268.png",
